<div class="w-container">
  <h2> FAQ</h2>
  <hr class="comments-rule"></hr>
  <h3>So how does it work? </h3>
  <p>We crowdsource and crowdfund garments that the Dapper Crowd wants from factories, makers and brands.  Once we reach our campaign goal for that garment we'll submit an order.<p>
  </br>

  <h3>How do I choose my size? </h3>
  <p> After crowdfunding a survey is sent requesting your sizing information. </p>
  </br>
  <h3>When will my garment ship? </h3>
  <p> Each campaign lists its shipping date. </p>
  </br>
  <h3>Can I exchange or return items after I receive it? </h3> 
  <p>Unlike most other companies, we don't carry inventory.  This helps us maintain low prices, but makes exchanges trickier.  We'll do our best to facilitate a return of unworn and unaltered items for a similar style or store credit.  Items marked final sale are not eligible for returns and exchanges.  If you have any questions please don't hesitate to email us.</p>
